                        "theory": "In morfologia si studiano le <span style='color: #2980b9; font-weight: bold;'>FORME DEL VERBO</span>.<br><br>Un verbo pu\u00f2 avere una forma:<br>\u2022 <span style='color: #27ae60; font-weight: bold;'>ATTIVA</span><br>\u2022 <span style='color: #c0392b; font-weight: bold;'>PASSIVA</span><br>\u2022 <span style='color: #e67e22; font-weight: bold;'>RIFLESSIVA</span><br>\u2022 <span style='color: #8e44ad; font-weight: bold;'>IMPERSONALE</span>.",
